The paper focuses on speech emotion recognition using deep learning techniques, which falls under the sub-categories of Speech and Dialogue Processing (cs.SD) and Computation and Language (cs.CL). The paper also utilizes transfer learning, which is a common technique in machine learning and falls under the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
